\pard{\pntext\f3\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf3\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'B7}}\ri-489\sa160\sl360\slmult1\qj\b Calculate cost: \b0 Calculates the cost of the trip between the destination and the starting point. \par
