{\pntext\f3\'B7\tab}\b Payment option:  \b0 The payment option must offer the choice of paying with wallets like Google Pay and Phone Pe, among others. \par
{\pntext\f3\'B7\tab}\b Download Invoice: \b0 The user will be given the opportunity to download the invoice for future use after it is generated..\par
{\pntext\f3\'B7\tab}\b Order Details: \b0 The Order page should have details about the previous orders of the customer and there should be an option for rating the cab driver after a successful ride. \par
{\pntext\f3\'B7\tab}\b Report Complaint: \b0 There should be an option to register the complaint or report the cab details to the admin.\par
{\pntext\f3\'B7\tab}\b Cancel the booked cab: \b0  Cancelation of the booked cab can be done there should have an option to cancel the order.after cancellation amount paid by user should be refunded to the user.\par

